The paper deals with information retrieval techniques to find appropriate news citations for statements in Wikipedia pages. This falls under the domain of natural language processing and information retrieval, which are covered by sub-categories such as cs.IR (Information Retrieval), cs.CL (Computation and Language), and cs.DL (Digital Libraries). Additionally, the paper also involves data management and database systems, which are covered by sub-categories such as cs.DB (Databases) and cs.CY (Computers and Society).
